# WrappingSubtractable - Protocol for types that support wrapping subtraction (-%)
module Core

### Defines the protocol `WrappingSubtractable`.
protocol WrappingSubtractable
  ### Implements the wired routine behavior for this value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$sub_wrap(you: Me) -> Me
